content.detailedDescription:
-i was at work driving in southborough, ma.
-i always look at the sky when i'm outside and i noticed this weird object i've never seen before.
-at first i bought it was just a plane. but there was no airport near me at all for it to be visible for a plane.
-it was a orb like object kinda fuzzy and round. seemed to have a light in the middle of it. it was moving straight slow and then went behind a cloud and all of a sudden started going the completely opposite direction. planes can't turn that fast.
-i was in shock and really surprised. i am a firm believer in extraterrestrial and studying biology in school. but i've never seen anything like this.
-it ended up going behind another really small cloud and then i never saw it come out from behind the cloud. so i looked around and i found it like 50 feet in front of the cloud. like it teleported or something. and then i couldn't see it anymore. it was gone.
content.summary: Was driving looking at the sky and behind a building into a field i saw this strange object

content.detailedDescription: i was driving from vidalia, la. west toward alexandria la. somewhere in the time frame of 3pm when i left vidalia. the highway was 2 lane and very few vehicles were traveling the road. i noticed two jet trails in the west that were very odd. there were jets going different directions and their trails would dissapate. the two i was watching remained the same, always the same width, length, and angle. other jets were flying this way, that way, and within minutes their vapor trails would dissapate the two of these objects stayed exactly the same. i watched this go on and on as i made my way toward alexandria. it is a long straight highway, so i was just curious as to what was going on. it's getting latter in the afternoon, and i'm getting closer to alexandria when i enter trees on the right side of the highway, when i drive out of the trees, there is a field, now i have a perfect view of one of the objects. it's not on the ground, but something like tree top high off the ground. in the middle there is a large brown circular object that has dents, or indentions. in a wide ban around the center of the ufo there are other different size brown objects that are the same color and makeup, but not as large. these objects are just motionless, and there is like a grey or brown mass around the entire ufo. it appeared as if the boulder objects were suspended in a spider web looking material. i was really close and extremely scared, i was glad that the highway turned south at this exact time. i was just outside of alexandria, and in couple of minutes i was in the edge of traffic. i know other people had to have witnessed this but i never heard a word about this from any source. i saw this many other afternoon's. too many to put into words, but not one thing was ever said or printed. the last time i saw this thing was probably dec.2013
content.summary: Some saturn like system with objects suspended around center

content.detailedDescription:
Last night my wife and i went outside to witness the conjunction of venus and jupiter. i set up my meade etx 90 with a 26mm lens. i took a couple of pictures of the full moon with my galaxy s4 using a film negative to negate the brightness of the moon in the eyepiece. after viewing the moon for 10 to 15 minutes, i turned my telescope on the conjunction.
i looked thru the eyepiece to make sure that i had them centered as my wife had never had a chance to look at planetary objects via a telescope. i showed her both planets and with jupiter you could see 3 of it's moons coming off at the 7 o'clock position and one at the 1 o'clock. theses appeared as small pinpoint objects. i had just taken over the eyepiece once again, and as i looked at the conjunction a pinpoint, pulsating or rapidly blinking light flew thru my view behind jupiter. unfortunately the occurrence happened so quickly i didn't have a chance of getting a pic of it. after it passed thru my field of view i quickly looked up with my naked eye to see if i could make it out (the red pinpoint), but it was not to be found in the sky. i can't even begin to describe the speed of what i saw, nor what it could have been. the one thing that i am definitely sure of is that it flew behind jupiter. the rest of the evening was quiet with the normal air traffic for our area of los angeles.
content.summary: Blinking red pin point light passed behind jupiter

content.detailedDescription:
The r/s was out on her porch near boucherie road, looking west, when she saw a large, bright object in the sky.

“it was very bright, it was definitely not a star,”  “this thing was big.”

she said it wasn’t completely circular, but had a tail off the end of it.

 it was very high in the sky and stationary for some time. then it disappeared.

“it didn’t stay there, a star stays in the sky,”
content.summary: It wasn’t completely circular, but had a tail off the end of it

content.detailedDescription:
This information is being transcribed from information gathered from the witness via a phone call from netherlands by investigator david kreiter.  
  the witness stated that when she was eleven years of age,she was riding with her father, a milkman, headed in a westerly direction on a highway near davenport,iowa. it was just before dawn when she looked to her right and saw a shiny silver disk-like object in the northern sky headed in a westerly direction. she watched it travel at a steady pace and then change direction and ascend at a 45 degree angle.
  she remembered the date because it was on the same day as the november 9th 1968 5.5 magnitude earthquake centered in illinois on the new madrid fault line.
content.summary: A shiny silver disk moved at a steady pace and then headed off at a 45 degree angle.

content.detailedDescription: Heading in from a fishing charter, it was sunset. looking up at the sky a huge cigar shaped object as big as a cruise ship appeared. the craft was invisible then glitches or blinked on and off a few times until it stayed on. it stayed in one spot completely visible. the craft appeared to be made of shiny metal with 4rows of windows. after staying on or visible in one spot for 30seconds, it shoot straight west.

content.detailedDescription: I was returning home in rancho cucamonga california on 06/30/2015 at 2300 pst. i stepped out of my automobile and looked northward and observed what appeared to be a bright orange star or planet approximately 40 degrees above the horizon. it was not moving and i had enough time to set up a small telescope i have in my garage. however, by the time that i had a proper alignment, the object loss intensity and faded in color. my last observation of it was a descending motion of one or two degrees, then it vanished away. i think what i saw was a flare, but it must have been at a very high altitude. strangest thing i've seen around here.
content.summary: I was viewing the northern sky and saw an orange star or planet.

content.detailedDescription: I drive a cab at night in the city of galesburg. at approximately 12:40 am on 24th of june i had pulled over into the back parking lot behind the 4l plaza (261 n. broad st.) to streach my legs. i spent a minute or so walking around behind the car and was headed back towards the front of the car when i looked up to stare at a radio tower located 35-40 ft. in front of. as i was looking at the top of the tower i noticed movement  out of the corner of my eye. i then saw what i thought was a plane at first off to east moving west on a straight path. it quickly realized it  was in the shape of a v, so i thought maybe a stealth bomber. but then i could see it wasn't a plane but was actually 6-10 objects flying in a v formation. i then thought to myself it must be a flock of geese? but as it got closer i could see no flapping wings and there formation was way too precise to be geese. as the got a little closer i could see they where all perfect spheres. they looked to silvery metallic at first like huge steel ball bearings. but then turned transparent right bout the time they got directly above my location. i could bearly see them, just like thier spherical outline and some of the link ghts from the city below would reflect off of them as they passed. i then thought to myself that this must be some top secret new aircraft. maybe like a new type of drone? then just before they disappeared behind the cloud off to the west several of the objects quickly switched places back and forth in the formation. there movement was so quick and so precise when they did so that chills ran down my spine, because i just knew that nothing man made could manuvore like that. i was left frozen in place and shaking my head in disbelief. i could not fathum what i just saw. i don't think i was the only one to see it. because 20 minutes later after i droped off another fair i noticed a group of  6-7 people standing in the save-a-lot parking lot staring and point in the direction of where i saw the objects. one of they was even holding thire phone up in the air like they where using to capture a video or take pictures maybe?
content.summary: 6-10 spherical transparent objects flying in v formation. several objects randomly switch places in the form at in

content.detailedDescription: On our way home from bethel one night, brother in law was driving the snow machine my mother rode behind him, i was being pulled in a sled behind them both. as i was facing foreward i seen a light from behind me start getting brighter. i remember thinking it was another snow machine getting ready to pass us as this happens on the shortcut we take on a regular basis. as i looked back to check out the source of the light i was surprised to see the light not on the ground level but about 20 feet up and about thirty feet back pacing our speed. there were no noise from roters or any downwash as you'd have from a helicopter. the light was bright so bright but it didn't cast its light beyond me in the sled it sat focused on me for what seemed like eternity, i can see the outline of the ship, triangular boomerang like as it hovered silently pacing us. then the ship stopped and shot out and away faster than any aircraft ive ever seen. i'm not sure if they knew i was in the back of the sled when they came to check on us pretty sure i was just as surprised as they were.
content.summary: Bright and quiet, left as fast as it appeared.

content.detailedDescription: In  1980 i owned a cabover freightliner truck that was geared out at about 63 miles an hour. i had only one 100 gallon fuel tank the other one was disabled and it was only about half full,i was in nogales arizona picking up a load of tomatoes for houston texas. i stayed in a motel in nogales all night and got a good nights sleep,i  picked up my load about 2:30 p.M. i left nogales and was going to take the shortcut down highway 82 to i 10. after getting on highway 82 i got so sleepy i had to pull off the side of the road to a roadside park to take a nap. this was about 4 p.M. the next thing i remember is it 10 p.M. and i was stopped on the side of the road on highway 90 outside of san antonio texas 950 miles from where i stop in az. (note) when i realized where i was outside of san antonio i have 20 dollars in my pocket and still had the advanced check i received on the load.I still had the same amount of fuel when i left nogales and only went 75 miles on my speedometer. i call my mother and san antonio to meet me at the coffee shop and told her what happened, and as everybody else has she laughed at me.But when i showed her the timestamp on my shipping bill and the time it was now she just had a funny look on her face.Now that i've told you all my story, you will probably laugh too like art bell did when i tried to tell him about it.
content.summary: 911 miles  in 6hrs.

content.detailedDescription: I was 16 years old. my boyfriend and i were were at the park. about 100 feet away i saw a person. but it wasnt a person exacly. it was made of what looked like static. all different colors. it was standing in one place but it's body was moving around abnormaly fast. it's arms and it's legs. nobody can move that fast. i didn't say anything i just watched it, i was petrified. and i though my eyes were playing tricks on me. my boyfriend said, do you see that? it looks like a static man and it looks like it's dancing.I said omg yes. he confermed what i saw, i knew it was real. he said, do you wanna leave? i said yes. i think we left. i thought i saw a ghost and forgot about it. it was years later that i came across the book (the communion). at my mother's garage sale. and what i read in that book was exacly what i saw. there is a lot more to tell.
content.summary: Static person

content.detailedDescription: Stopped down by the river between bangor and brewer.  the bright light was noticed circling in a tight fast circle.  way to fast and tight turns for aircraft.  it kept the same flight path in circles above the clouds. it was almost right above the train bridge that crosses bangor and brewer.I have seen all military aircraft and none can make these turns at such a high speed.  the only noise was a distant humming noise but could have been coming from the city.  the light was so bright it shined perfect threw the clouds every spot it went.  it was not a spot light or airport light. after seeing this for 7 minutes i felt fatigued and nauseous.  after driving 5 miles outside of the city the sick feeling left.
content.summary: Light moving very fast above clouds circling to fast for aircraft.

content.detailedDescription:
I live in hillsboro, ohio.  i observed a ufo in march of 2015, in the sky above my town.  here is what occurred and what happened.  i do not have any video.

at approximately 7:15 pm, i was in a car that my wife was driving.  we stopped at a cvs drug store and she went inside to pick up a prescription.  i remained in the car in the parking lot.  i was just killing time looking around and i observed in the sky, in a southeast direction but pretty much overhead of my location, what appeared to be a bright star that that a yellowish tint to it.  i stared at it, wondering if it was a planet.  i had never seen a yellowish star before.  i looked at it for approximately 5-8 seconds.  then it just blinked out.  i thought maybe it had been covered by a cloud or something, so i kept looking at the same spot waiting for it to appear again.

but after that initial bright looking "star" disappeared.  six more of the exact same size, brightness and color, appeared in the same spot.  but these six "lights" were in a configuration that i could not and can not explain.

i do not know if these "lights' were six different objects in some kind of formation, or if all six lights were on one very large object.  i could not see any shape of or outline of what object these lights may have been attached too.

the six lights also only lasted approximately 5-8 seconds, then they all blinked out.  they had appeared simultaneously and blinked out simultaneously.  the entire time i observed the initial lone light and afterwards, the six lights.  these lights never moved.  they were all stationary the entire time.  which is strange in and of itself.   none of the lights ever pulsated or blinked.

i can get the exact date if it is needed.  i would just have to check with the pharmacy and see what day we picked up a "z-pack" from the pharmacy.  it should be in their records.

i have made a drawing of what i observed, and it is shown here in this email.

i should state some facts about me.  i am 62 years old.  i served 8 years in the marine corps, and i am a retired police lieutenant of the cleveland police department.  my vision is good, and i don't claim that this was some kind of alien spaceship.  i am only reporting what i observed, and stating that what i saw is not explainable by me.  in truth i am a pretty sharp fellow.  but i have no even remotely reasonable explanation for what i observed.

as i said earlier.  i could not see any detail of what these lights may have been attached too, or on.  but my impression at the time, was that they were on one large object, that was probably triangular in shape.  mostly because the alignment of the lights was so perfectly aligned.

maybe someone else reported something similar in my area, and if so.  please let me know.

here is my drawing of what i saw, but they were much lighter in color than my drawing:
content.summary: Stationary lights in a triangular formation.

content.summary: Me & 4 friends witnessed a round craft hovering high in sky with a bright blue ring around it we all looked up looked at each other  looked up again there was a super bright flash that blinded everyone when could see again was just a blue trail of light

content.detailedDescription:
The evening of friday april 10th, 2015 i noticed an intriguing appearance of what appears to be a red field of energy.  i had taken two videos, one at 8:18 p.M. and the other at 10:06 p.M.  the direction was nnw over blue springs lake at an elevation of about 18° from the horizon.

1.	 in the first one, while observing what appeared to be a blinking light flying nnw over blue springs lake, one can see a series of images of two lights, with an occasional streak.  the following are some of the images of the craft in the 1st video.  it may be possible that the bluish colored lines below the bright images are parts of a larger sphere which is only partly visible on occasion.  they resemble elements of the spheres that have been observed during the last eight months.  (frame 4:49) is a good example.
   
2.	the 2nd video  shows blinking lights that change morphologically during energy pulses.  the (frames :23 and :48) are some of the variations in which yellow-redish energy pulses take place.
          
then as the craft dissapeared from view in the second video, i noticed a red background field. it began with (frame 1:22).  it began very faintly, and then intensified by the end of it.  it is unclear what could be causing the energy field, but it does appear to be round.  

comparisons of red fields during 2nd video

analysis of the first video began after the second had been completed.  one can see a field intensifying from the 14-second mark.  it became so intense that there is little need to edit the (frame at 22:58)...  1/60th of a second later, frame 22:59, it disappeared and all was black.  then it reappeared again in frame 23:00 and was visible until the final frame in 23:10.

enhancement to the second video’s full view of the field in (frame 2:21) shows a full red energy sphere.  

as of now, there is no explanation of what the nature of this energy field is.  whether it is a craft, a portal, or a field that is generated remains unknown and only speculation at present is possible.  what is clear however is that it was present on two occasions and exhibits a tendency to intensify, to completely disappear, and to reappear again during filming. this is the only occasion in which this has been apparent thus far.
content.summary: Red energy field

content.detailedDescription: I was walking with my other half and noticed two lights in the sky that looked unusually bright.  one appeared to be a very bright star in the distance, and the other, a very large and very bright star with a hazy glow around it.  we both stopped to observe further, thinking it was an airplane that would soon come into view, as we live in a neighborhood with a heavy flight pattern for airplanes.  the two bright lights did not move or change direction.  the bigger and brighter light appeared to be bobbing. i took out my iphone to video it and when i looked at the video later on i noticed that the bigger bright light was pulsating and turned into a saturn-like ring. we continued to walk for 45 more minutes and the lights remained unchanged. definitely not a star or airplane!
content.summary: Two lights, both brighter than stars and the nearest one larger and brighter.

content.detailedDescription: This was possibly a meteorite or space junk falling to earth. i was in my front yard looking towards the east at the very bright moon. i turned to look over my house and i saw an amazing bright reddish light cruising across the sky going south west to north west. i wanted to run into my house to grab my camcorder but i knew i would not have time to get it. so i stayed and watched this light for about 20 more seconds as it finally faded away. the whole event lasted about 30 seconds.  i've seen satellites and the space station from my house and this was very different. the intensity of the light was brilliant..... nothing like i have seen before.
content.summary: Very bright reddish glowing object.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to work on a dark rainy night.As i went over a hill i noted an "airplane" flying slowly right over some homes across the small valley.I assumed it was a smaller plane because there was a row of approx. 6-7 round white lights along the "side" in a row.I knew it was going to crash because it was so low in a hilly area.I drove around a curve in the road and was startled to see the object was now right over the road in front of me.This was a matter of seconds and it had to have been at least a mile away.It was still and about 20ft off the road so i assumed it was a helicopter.I drove under it and stopped,opened my window and looked up.It was not a plane or a helicopter.It made no noise ,there was no downdraft.It was just dark with these lights.Nothing happened i just stared at it.I was worried about being late for work and eventually drove off with it still hovering over the road.Can not believe i left,i was very calm,not afraid at all,it was very surreal.The next day i noted that power lines were going across the road in the approximate area.It was definitely an object and not identifiable.From a distance it seemed to be about the size of a small passenger plane,when i was under it,it went beyond the sides of the 2 lane road so i could not see the length due to rain and dark.It is still a mystery to me to this day but i can still remember it all as though it were last month.No other cars were seen on the road before or after this incident.I did a sketch at the time that i am trying to locate.
content.summary: Observed across valley over homes,turned corner and it was over road,parked under it

content.detailedDescription:
It was a warm summer night in harbour grace nl canada, roughly twenty five years ago.  my friend was leaving the next day to head to alberta for work.  so rather than a party, another friend and i decided to just treat him to a beer and have a quiet evening, as he had an early morning flight.  we only had a couple of beers each, i think its important to specify this so no conclusions can be made that we were impaired in any way.  the three of us decided to sit on the dock at a local lake and just talk a bit, we were just saying good by to our friend.   
years before i had seen a movie where some kids were stuck in the desert, and a local kid was helping them survive and cross the desert, (i have no idea of the name of this movie, but i believe it may have been a disney movie).  anyway in one of the scenes, it was night time and the local kid sees an object moving through the sky, he points it out to the other kids and says the gods are moving in the sky.  the other kids  try and explain to him that no, its not the gods, it a satellite.  the movie showed the object and it looked like a star moving across the sky.  
back to my story, that night on the dock by the lake, i happened to notice the same thing, an object moving across the sky which looked like a star.  you could easily tell this thing was extremely high, not an aircraft such as a helicopter, as i said it looked like a star, plus there was no sound.  i said to myself cool, it must be a satellite on a polar orbit, just like i had seen in that movie years ago.  i knew it was a polar orbit as it was heading from south to north.  i watched this thing move north for perhaps a minute.  we were sitting facing west, it was perhaps 15 degrees west of us, not directly overhead.  i picked it up when it was perhaps 30 degrees south west of us and i followed it until it was roughly about 15 degrees north west of us.  it was at this point that it stopped, it did not slow down, it just stopped.  this is when i spoke, at the same time, my friend who was leaving in the morning also spoke, exclaiming at the same time, holy $()/&, did you see that, he had been following it as well.  for the next minute or so we were trying to point out this "star" to our other friend who had not seen it.  where it had stopped in the sky was directly next to another "star", while still trying to point out this thing to our other friend, it started moving again just as fast as before.  only this time it was not heading north, it was heading north east, it changed direction by about 40-45 degrees from its original course.  as incredible as that was, the star that it had stopped by, well that one started moving as well.  that one headed north west.  it was at this point that, when they started moving again that our other friend picked them up.  we followed them as long as we could but they blurred with the other stars and disappeared.   
that is my story, perhaps it can be explained, perhaps not, i just figured it was time to share it.
content.summary: Star like objects moving across sky then changing directions.

content.summary: Bright round hovered made sharp turn then disappeared

clip briufo : 2 ufo's  i lightened the movie in imovie. i have the original if you request it, it's just easier for you to see, less fussing around. all i did was increase  the exposure.

content.detailedDescription:
On june 26, 2015 between approximately 11:34om to 11:42pm i witnessed a ufo. below is the description of the event:

after driving through pimlico dr in mechanicsville virginia, i noticed in the east a red-orange fireball behind the tree line flying west with a very slight northward bearing.

i turned and parked in christopher paul dr, i observed no breeze or windy conditions with a scattered and partially overcast sky. the object was flying below the clouds as it was bright and clear. the object had no sound, appeared to be going about the speed of a prop plane and wobbled as it flew. my view became obstructed by rooftops and after i moved further away from the houses to get a better view, the object's light faded out. i estimate the object flew at least as far as i-295 somewhere north of the pole green rd exit.

i used the sky guide app and found out there were no satellites or rockets of any kind during that time frame.
content.summary: Pole green area, mechanicsville va ufo

content.detailedDescription: A friend and i were driving on rt 15 on a cloudy rainy night. we saw a low flying o brecht the size of a city block flying slowly over the highway. we pulled over and got out to get a better view even though it was a busy freeway. the rectangular craft hovered but emitted a relatively quiet jet like sound. there were no rotor blades nor colored lights as required by faa. as the craft slowly hovered nearby and almost over our heads, it shone beams of white light at the ground. i thought surely it had seen us and was expecting to be illuminated by the random light beams to the ground, but that never happened. then the craft suddenly moved off at nearly instantaneous speed and disappeared into the clouds. my friend and i never discussed it as we got back in the car and proceeded on our way. there was no desire to tell anyone until now.
content.summary: City block sized craft, hovering, light beams, jet noise, extremely fast departure

content.detailedDescription: On a clear day with no wind at 12:43pm i observed a prop plane fly overhead, it was turning from the southwest to the southeast. it was then when i noticed one white orb flying closely along side to the right of the plane. the orb was smaller than the plane and appeared to be "locked in" with the path of the plane. observed until view was obstructed by buildings and trees. the event lasted about two minutes.
content.summary: Orb ufo near hanover airpark, ashland virginia
